{"title": "It\u2019s easier to keep star employees than to sue them for leaving", "tags": "business", "timestamp": "2024-04-13", "content": "If bosses don\u2019t want their most talented employees to quit and join their competitors, there is one practical step they can take \u2013 treat them so well that they would never think of leaving.\nIt is futile to take legal options such as putting strict anti-competitive terms in their employment contracts, because the law frowns at attempts to curb the freedom of employees to further their careers."}